Summary: Very large, no flashing lights, flying close to the ground
divs: Sighting DetailsThis is not a report of a recent sighting. As a matter of fact I am looking for information. I am wondering if it is worthwhile reporting an up close sighting that occured in 1959. I have been holding on to this for a long however I wish to report it if it is of any use to anyone. If you get a chance could I be advised. Thank You
